sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Component / Guard
    participant V as Local View
    participant D as Diagnostic Classifier
    participant R as Diagnostic Report
    participant S as Diagnostics Surface
    participant T as Tests / Readiness Gate

    C->>V: observe state / expected condition
    C->>D: compare expected vs observed
    D->>D: classify category + severity
    D->>R: create report
    R->>S: publish diagnostic evidence
    R->>T: support validation / readiness
    Note over R,S: Report does not mutate runtime behavior by itself.
